tchr

Connectivity tables (w/o time-reversal symmetry)

The tables below give the minimum band connectivity, νᵀ, of transverse photonic bands required by symmetry without the presence of time-reversal symmetry. See the time-reversal invariant tables for context and notational details.

SG 1

[Trivial symmetry indicator group, ℤ₁]

1st minimal solution: νᵀ = 2 (1 symmetry vector)

nᵀ
[2R₁, 2T₁, 2U₁, 2V₁, 2X₁, 2Y₁, 2Z₁, (▪)2T]

2nd minimal solution: νᵀ = 3 (1 symmetry vector)
